code: import axios from'axios';import{URL}from'../constants/urls';const getAll=async()=>{const weatherHistory=await axios.get(URL.WEATHERHISTORY);return weatherHistory.data;};const create=async cityName=>{const newCity={city:cityName};const result=await axios.post(URL.WEATHERHISTORY,newCity);return result.data;};const remove=()=>{return axios.delete(URL.WEATHERHISTORY);};export default{getAll,create,remove};
